{
  "texts": [
    "A codebook was developed based on search keywords (Table 1).",
    "An initial meeting was scheduled for researchers to clarify the definitions of the codes.",
    "The same 100 tweets were coded by three researchers and achieved inter-rater reliability of 96%.",
    "Note that a degree of agreement was accepted when codes belonged to the same level-1 category.",
    "A follow-up meeting was held to discuss disagreement, \"Policy\" and \"Attitude\" codes were added to better answer the research questions."
  ]
}